Gimmix-0.2 README
====================

Gimmix is a graphical Music player daemon (MPD) client written in C
using Gtk+2.

Features:
* Simple and cleanInterface.
* System tray icon support.
* Playlist browser.
* Playlist search.
* Notification support (Display the currently playing song in systray).
* Small memory footprint.

Requirements:
* gtk+-2.10.x
* libglade-2.6.x
* libmpd-0.12
* libconfuse-2.5
* libnotify-0.4.x
* taglib-1.4 (C bindings)

Installation:
Read the INSTALL file for details on installation procedure.

Configuration:
Gimmix stores its configuration settings in ~/.gimmixrc

Bugs:
If you encounter any bug(s), please e-mail the authour at priyankmg@gmail.com
with a detailed description and steps to reproduce the bug. It would be
good if you mention your version of linux, gtk, libmpd etc.


